  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: 9th-level warlock, Pact of the Tome feature</em><br />Immediately after a creature casts a spell that targets you or includes you in its area of effect, you can use your reaction to make an ability check using your warlock spellcasting ability. On a success, you steal the knowledge of the spell if it is at least 1st level and of a level you can cast (it can be a spell from any spell list). For the next 8 hours or until you use this feature again, you know the spell and can cast it using your spell slots. The DC equals 10 + the spell's level.</p>",
